f2e6360 Fix waitlist revert bug by normalizing OAuth emails to lowercase
 apps/web/src/server/auth.ts | 16 ++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 16 insertions(+)
commit f2e63601774a51d8d9c091700c2324a1161815d2
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Mon Jan 5 18:28:53 2026 +0000

    Fix waitlist revert bug by normalizing OAuth emails to lowercase

    OAuth providers (GitHub, Google) were storing emails with their original
    casing, while email magic link sign-in lowercases emails. This caused
    case-sensitive email lookups to fail, creating new waitlisted accounts
    instead of recognizing existing users.

    Added profile callbacks to both OAuth providers to normalize emails to
    lowercase, ensuring consistent email comparison across all auth methods.

